 Women who were subjected to fetal scalp sampling are asked to fill in a questionnaire within 24 hours after delivery.

 The questionnaire deals with how the woman experienced the testing procedure.

 Physicans who performed the test are asked to fill in a questionnaire within 24 hours after delivery.

 The questionnaire deals with how the physician experienced the testing procedure.

